EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
AZORES TO UNITED KINGDOM.
EIGHT METER VESSEL HARRIER IS DOWN, YELLOW HULL,
ONE PERSON ON BOARD, UNREPORTED AZORES
TO UNITED KINGDOM. VESSELS IN VICINITY
REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT,
ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO MRCC FALMOUTH,
PHONE: 44 132 631 7575, FAX: 44 132 631 5610,
E-MAIL: FALMOUTHCOASTGUARD@MCGA.GOV.UK.
